FBIS4-7216 "dreas082_a_94041" FBIS-EAS-94-082 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Defense Agency Cancels New Chief's U.S. Visit Defense Agency Cancels New Chief's U.S. Visit OW2804081194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0804 GMT 28 Apr 94 OW2804081194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, April 28 KYODO -- The Defense Agency on Thursday canceled a visit to the U.S. by the agency chief slated for May 1 due to a change in the Japanese cabinet, agency officials said. Since Defense Agency chief Kazuo Aichi was replaced by Atsushi Kanda, there is not enough time for preparations for the trip, agency officials said.
